title: The New York City Roast Session Show 2 With Karlous Miller DCYoungFly & Chico Bean | Ep. 156

description:
For Live Show Tickets https://www.85southshow.com/live/ For tickets to the 2nd Chicago Live Show: https://www.ticketfly.com/purchase/ev... The 85 South Show took the live show to New York for two sold out shows and you know they roasted everybody, created a couple freestyle improv songs off the dome and kept the jokes coming all night long. DC Young Fly, Karlous Miller and Chico Bean cover everything from The New York City projects to winning the lottery, and the crew covers it all while bringing the laughs, in the second sold out show from The Big Apple! These standup comedians brought the house down two times in NYC!
